title: EXCLUSIVE Kinda Funny Live 2 Merch Trailer!
description:
Get your tickets NOW! http://www.kindafunny.com/tickets


Designs by pandamusk: https://twitter.com/pandamusk

Designs by Andy Cortez: https://twitter.com/MaximumCortez

transcript_chunks.text: What's up guys? I want to tell you all about the exclusive merch that will be at Kinda Funny Live. First off, we got the official Kinda Funny Live poster designed by PandaMusk. There will be 300 of these bad boys available. Now check out the official KFL tour shirt. There will also be 300 of these available. You need this in your life. Next up, we're about to get real exclusive. Andy Cortez designed us a KF In Sync design that I love so much. We're selling a shirt and a poster. There will only be 150 shirts and 100 posters, so make sure that if you want this, you get it quick. Also limited to 150 is Andy C's badass Kinda Funny Live Street Fighter shirt. I can't wait to see this all over your bodies. The most elusive thing is every single VIP ticket holder gets an exclusive signed poster designed by the amazing PandaMusk. The only way to get this is to be VIP, and you know what? You guys have requested it, and you've been so nice to us. The Kinda Funny Aerobics Championship shirt will be

by the amazing PandaMusk. The only way to get this is to be VIP, and you know what? You guys have requested it, and you've been so nice to us. The Kinda Funny Aerobics Championship shirt will be back in full effect, so now you have your second chance to get one. So there you go. I want to make sure everyone prepared going in. If you already have your ticket, I can't wait to see you. If not, head over to KindaFunny.com/tickets and get yours now.
